const labelColors = { complete: 'success', pending: 'warning', rejected: 'error' }; const Table1 = () => ( )} title="Latest Orders" /> Number Customer Items Total Status Date {orders.map((order) => ( {order.number} {order.customer.name} {order.items} {numeral(order.totalAmount) .format(`${order.currency}0,0.00`)} {format(order.createdAt, 'dd MMM, yyyy HH:mm:ss')} ))}
